abstract: >-
  AAFC Bioinformatics Code Catalogue (ABCC) template repository provides a modular and 
  extensible framework for developing reproducible data analysis pipelines within the 
  [AAFC-Bioinfo-AAC](https://github.com/AAFC-Bioinfo-AAC?view_as=public) GitHub organization. 
  It enables researchers and developers to quickly set up new projects using parameterized,
  reusable components that can be easily adapted to diverse use cases.

